          p James has worked in the real estate industry for a total of 15 years, including 8 years of commercial real estate appraisal experience. Most recently, Mr. Dunne served as a Vice President at CBRE in their Valuation &amp; Advisory Services group. Mr. Dunne has appraised a wide variety of property types including multifamily, office, industrial, self-storage facilities, retail centers, mixed-use properties and development sites. His clients include commercial banks, pension funds, private equity, government institutions, attorneys and developers.

